?\nIs this your car out front?\nI jumped the kerb.\nMaybe we could...\ntake care of it ourselves.\nIf you wanna call the cops, that's okay, too...\n- I guess. - No.\nNo cops.\nThank you.\n(CLATTERS)\n(KARPOV STRAINING)\nYou have kept your looks, Colonel.\nCongratulations.\n\"Mission report. December 16, 1991.\"\nWho are you?\nMy name is Zemo.\nI will repeat my question.\nMission report, December 16, 1991.\nHow did you find me?\nWhen S.H.I.E.L.D. fell...", "type": "Document"}}